## Cache Key Patterns

### Standard Patterns

```ruby
# Simple key
['articles', 'list']

# With timestamp
['articles', 'list', Article.maximum(:updated_at)]

# With user
['articles', 'list', Current.user.id]

# With date
['articles', 'trending', Date.today]

# With version
['articles', 'list', 'v2']

# Complex key
['dashboard', Current.user.id, Date.today, 'v1']

# Model-based
[model, 'attribute', value]
[@article, 'reading_time']
[@article, 'related_articles', 5]
```

